{"tid":2054193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉淑儀：將來審理「港區國安法」案件不宜安排陪審員","createTime":"2020-06-07T03:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T05:28:57.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5bf89744de2eb0d2bf13cbed543371bacbcfe558","tid":2054193,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀表示，將來審理涉及「港區國安法」的案件，不適合安排陪審員審訊，因陪審員會有很多不同理由拒絕參與審訊。<br />\n<br />\n曾任保安局局長的葉劉淑儀，出席一個電台節目後，回應當年推動《基本法》23條立法時，後期於條例草案加入必須有陪審員審訊的建議，但現時認為不適合是否因擔心社會氣氛改變，不少人對立法反感，如設陪審團對案件不利。葉劉淑儀說，過去本港極少審理涉及國家安全的案件，加上陪審團可能會驚被「起底」，因此認為不適合。"},{"pid":"42f77644790bc5a5df2936deaaa1081d9d6837da","tid":2054193,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:30:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530658-20200607.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530658-20200607.htm&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=dca0ac32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530658-20200607.htm&h=ff3e7866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530658-20200607.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3245c78562ecd0517d3887086c8a5b0de3c7b629","tid":2054193,"uid":266342,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"呢個仆街啦真係唔死都冇用<br />\n完全將普通法唔知擺咗去邊"},{"pid":"8f789b894f462dccfa071dbb2e5666b7e207fe1b","tid":2054193,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3245c78562ecd0517d3887086c8a5b0de3c7b629","tid":2054193,"uid":266342,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"呢個仆街啦真係唔死都冇用<br />\n完全將普通法唔知擺咗去邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:31:44.000Z","msg":"無人打算普通法<br />\n會盡快一國一制"},{"pid":"b02f8622616da0beb0e753c89169e1a24ba5c4e4","tid":2054193,"uid":237300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"r